{"tid":687121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡殯儀館地下滲水 港鐵認無簽紙即落石屎","createTime":"2018-06-02T03:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T03:59:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edb3b785ac3fc28bd1abda86616163f95568cd2c","tid":687121,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180602/s00006/5df89d16c5015f47d9c08146f10af3f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180602%2Fs00006%2F5df89d16c5015f47d9c08146f10af3f1.jpg&h=cec53c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】除了紅磡站擴建月台工程被揭發鋼筋接駁造假，沙中線紅磡站北面連接隧道的接駁位亦同樣被揭發鋼筋接駁有問題，導致嚴重滲水。立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰昨日向就有關工程，詢問港鐵有否跟足程序「檢查簽紙後，先落石屎」；港鐵工程總監黃唯銘回應稱，整項沙中線工程有超過1萬個地方需要檢查鋼筋後簽紙才可落石屎，惟涉事隧道（即殯儀館下方）較彎曲，承認有一小段地方「做得不足」，承建商沒有港鐵簽紙批核便已落石屎。<br />\n<br />\n3鋼筋接駁位未達標&ensp;拆石屎重新施工<br />\n<br />\n港鐵在提交予立法會的文件上承認，工程人員去年8月確定紅磡站北面連接隧道工程出現滲水，並深入檢查，其間承建商曾採取打針防漏法及灌漿等多項止漏措施，但由於滲水持續，工程人員今年2月鑿開連接位混凝土的表面，發現連接位的鋼筋接駁未達施工標準；其後港鐵進一步檢查同一地盤的連接位，發現整個地盤有3個接駁位置出現問題，均由同一承建商建造，港鐵已立即要求承建商採取補救措施，包括拆除出現問題的接駁鋼筋混凝土，並重新施工。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰倡設獨立委會調查挽信心<br />\n<br />\n田北辰表示，港鐵承認有部分位置「原來無人簽紙，就倒石屎」，認為是絕對不能接受，憂慮其他地方可能出現同類問題，亦會令公眾失去信心，「整項沙中線有超過1萬個地方需要簽紙，大家又如何知道港鐵是否做足？」他要求政府設獨立委員會調查沙中線工程問題，以釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180602/s00001/1527876625563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180602%2Fs00001%2F1527876625563&d=%2BH8AeSx0EdIs1l%2BlHnIxP8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=eeb07b7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180602%2Fs00001%2F1527876625563&h=fc0bcdfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180602/s00001/1527876625563</a>"},{"pid":"03de59258eb7bb0fd98702c5202c1077dbe48d47","tid":687121,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"公眾一早無左信心"},{"pid":"38a17417211e9a7dc6d29822576f68baa637c3f4","tid":687121,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2015.11/2015.11.17/airline/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2015.11%2F2015.11.17%2Fairline%2F01.jpg&h=b238c6e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a044cb09a20d13a5d1cf386a67f271bd1c4620c3","tid":687121,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"第日高鐵出事死人直接送過去大酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f035eb0fffa909f79421f42f8ee30e8e7d20cac","tid":687121,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7c122a99b1dcb3de590e32dbaaa1de75f40fb5","tid":687121,"uid":37003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c114c6427c8805849e64f79d7c660a4e4e57506","tid":687121,"uid":66908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f035eb0fffa909f79421f42f8ee30e8e7d20cac","tid":687121,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"唔好衝出黎柒，呢個位都係1112禮記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f677063bb2856d69ed741c1b766c9fde06536208","tid":687121,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{